nodes.bodyText:
I wonder if we should actually be a bit more lenient about this and take the longest array at the given dimension?
In PostgreSQL this is a limitation of the array type itself:
=# select array[ array[1, 2],  array[3, 4, 5] ];
ERROR:  2202E: multidimensional arrays must have array expressions with matching dimensions

@kovrus what do you think?

